# This static site needs no secrets to build or run.
#
# basePath is derived automatically from GITHUB_REPOSITORY during the GitHub
# Actions build, so you do not set it by hand. To preview a project-site
# basePath locally, you can run:
#
#   GITHUB_REPOSITORY=you/your-repo npm run build
#
# Copy this file to .env.local only if you add integrations later.
